  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK960">
<l>nalamvēṇṭi ṉāṇuṭaimai vēṇṭuṅ kulamvēṇṭiṉ</l>
<l>vēṇṭuka yārkkum paṇivu</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>He who desires a good name must desire modesty and he who desires (the continuance of) a family greatness must be submissive to all.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
